Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: "...L'Isle-Adam... Data missing. Forget about it. Chrome, your frame has been modified again. How do you feel?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: "You're a great prospect. I understand the mission was given by Hassen, but you haven't forgotten who you should report to, have you?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'I will perform my duty and report the results according to the guidelines.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: 'Have you confirmed the route of "that ship"?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: 'The destination port has been located. We deciphered the remaining data from the early Golden Age and expect the "ship" to pull in at 7:00 tonight.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nikola', 3: "Just keep your team on a tight leash. Don't let them...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Eh? It went through! I knew spamming the team channel would work!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "What's up, Captain? You don't look too good. Are there Corrupted nearby? Don't worry, I'll be there soon!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Chrome', 3: '...No. Did you get lost again, Kamui?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "I'm already at the port! Where are you? It's all dark in here...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Ah! Right... Wait, there's a bunch of sneaky machines... Hmm? I can't seem to detect any Corrupted nearby...", 4: '1'}
